summary: hey guys ! ive decided to start taking commissions again with adjusted pricing . im also taking them in slots of 3 , so hmu asap...
caption:
hey guys ! ive decided to start taking commissions again with adjusted pricing . im also taking them in slots of 3 , so hmu asap if youre interested !

commissions are officially open again ! (5/20)

please provide reference . descriptions of characters should be detailed . will correct sketches twice before charging extra (additional charges will depend on the magnitude of the change(s) requested) .

contact me over tumblr (via ask/messenger) if you are interested in a commission . do not pay for a commission without discussing it with me . i will send you an invoice and thus require you send me your paypal .

any money sent to my paypal without my approval will be seen as a donation .

paypal: SpoiledCitrus@hotmail.com

will do:

  • mild n/s/f/vv
  • furries
  • monsters
  • most things , probably

wont do:

  • wildly complex machinery
  • ask if you are unsure
